New ECB Role in EFSF May be ‘Difficult,’ Rehn Tells Handelsblatt

-- B y   B r i a n   P a r k i n
-- 
2011-10-21T05:16:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/new-ecb-role-in-efsf-may-be-difficult-rehn-tells-handelsblatt.html
Enrolling the  European Central Bank 
to help boost the firepower of the European bailout fund may be
difficult, the European Union’s Economic Commissioner Olli Rehn
said in a Handelsblatt interview.  ‘Indeed we must be careful what the EU treaty allows and
what it doesn’t. A direct link between ECB refinancing and the
EFSF could be difficult,’’ Rehn is cited as saying.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Brian Parkin at 
 bparkin@bloomberg.net  